0.8.0

	* libmdtk: improved neighbor lists update procedure
	* libmdtk: new space-saving file format for storing MD system configurations
	* libmdtk: optional 'hemispherical' thermal bath geometry
	* mdtrajview: ability to save rotational transformations
	* mdtrajview: unified visualization of 'halo' bombardment areas
	* mdtrajsim, mdtrajview: more flexible command line options processing
	* Bugfixes

0.7.0

	* libmdtk: improved simulation core, speedup ~3-8 times
	* mdtrajview: interactive simulation
	* build-system: mingw cross compiling
	* build-system: partial FLTK 1.3 support
	* Bugfixes
